Web Scraping Based AI Chatbot (Console Application)

A Python-based console chatbot that scrapes website content and uses OpenAI GPT models to answer user queries strictly based on the scraped data.

This project demonstrates the integration of web scraping, prompt engineering, and LLM-based conversational AI.

ğŸ“Œ Features

ğŸŒ Scrapes live website content using requests and BeautifulSoup

